---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import OrnamentalDivider from '../components/OrnamentalDivider.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="How Alone in the Dungeon handles your data."
>
  <section class="relative mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 pt-20 pb-10 text-center">
    <h1 class="candleglow font-pixel text-4xl text-glow-50 md:text-5xl">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 font-sans text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-mist-500">Last updated: 1 July 2026</p>
    <OrnamentalDivider class="mx-auto mt-8 w-44 text-violet-500" />
  </section>

  <div class="prose-body mx-auto max-w-[var(--container-prose)] px-6 pb-16">
    <p>
      Alone in the Dungeon (<strong>aloneinthedungeon.com</strong>) is operated by Matt Gilbert. This policy explains what information is collected when you use this site and how it is used.
    </p>

    <h2>What we collect</h2>
    <p>
      This site uses Google Analytics 4 to collect anonymised usage data — pages visited, approximate location, device type, and referral source. This data is used to understand how the site is used and to improve it. Google Analytics sets cookies in your browser to track sessions. You can opt out using <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google's opt-out browser add-on</a>.
    </p>
    <p>
      The only other personal data collected is what you voluntarily submit through the contact form: your name, email address, and message.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact form</h2>
    <p>
      Contact form submissions are processed by <a href="https://www.netlify.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Netlify</a> and delivered to the site owner by email. Netlify's own <a href="https://www.netlify.com/privacy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">privacy policy</a> applies to the processing of form data on their infrastructure. We do not sell, share, or otherwise distribute your contact information. Messages are used solely to respond to your enquiry.
    </p>
    <p>
      You may request deletion of any message you have sent by emailing <a href="mailto:matt@hobbinomicon.com">matt@hobbinomicon.com</a>.
    </p>

    <h2>Embedded content</h2>
    <p>
      Some posts embed YouTube videos. YouTube is operated by Google LLC and is subject to <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google's privacy policy</a>. This site uses the <code>youtube-nocookie.com</code> domain for embeds where possible to reduce third-party tracking.
    </p>

    <h2>External links</h2>
    <p>
      This site links to external websites. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of those sites and encourage you to read their policies before submitting any personal information.
    </p>

    <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
    <p>
      This policy may be updated from time to time. The date at the top of this page reflects the most recent revision.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Questions about this policy: <a href="mailto:matt@hobbinomicon.com">matt@hobbinomicon.com</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
